(168, 1, '2017-06-04 05:58:42', '2017-06-04 05:58:42', '<strong>Women’s Legal Service Queensland has appointed an experienced family lawyer as its new CEO.</strong><br><br>\r\nThe organisation announced recently that it has named Angela Lynch (pictured) as its new leader.\r\n\r\nMs Lynch has over 23 years’ experience in family and domestic violence law. She has a long history of involvement with WLSQ, and was appointed to the Queensland Domestic and Family Violence Death Review and Advisory Board in 2016.', 'Women’s legal service appoints chief executive', '', 'publish', 'closed', 'closed', '', 'news-1', '', '', '2017-06-08 11:07:22', '2017-06-08 11:07:22', '', 0, 'http://35.154.128.159:83/?post_type=all_news&#038;p=168', 0, 'all_news', '', 0),
