se Terms, and any attempt to do so will be void. RA may assign its rights to any of its affiliates or subsidiaries, or to any successor in interest of any business associated with the Services.</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<h3 style="font-size: 19px;">20. Questions and contact information</h3>\r\n<p style="margin-bottom: 35px;">All questions or comments about the Site or its contents should be directed to <a href="mailto:contact@rightadvice.ae."> contact@rightadvice.ae. </a></p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'Terms Of Use', '', 'inherit', 'closed', 'closed', '', '108-revision-v1', '', '', '2018-03-23 06:25:11', '2018-03-23 06:25:11', '', 108, 'http://35.154.128.159:83/blog/2018/03/23/108-revision-v1/', 0, 'revision', '', 0),
